 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">4. Cost Comparison: Silicon vs. GaN V</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">While GaN V chargers carry a 20-35% unit cost premium over silicon equivalents, the total cost of ownership often favors GaN V when shipping, returns, and brand positioning are factored in:</p>
